definitions.definition: Any of four closely related genera ( Dendrocitta , Crypsirina , Temnurus and as of recently also Platysmurus ) of arboreal long-tailed passerine birds in the subfamily Crypsirininae of the family Corvidae .

main_definition: Any of four closely related genera ( Dendrocitta , Crypsirina , Temnurus and as of recently also Platysmurus ) of arboreal long-tailed passerine birds in the subfamily Crypsirininae of the family Corvidae .
